<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.10.9">
<l>paṇṇi ṉaippaṇṇil niṉṟatōr pāṉmaiyaip pāluḷ neyyiṉai māluru vāyniṉṟa</l>
<l>viṇṇi ṉaiviḷaṅ kumcuṭarc cōtiyai vēḷvi yaiviḷak kiṉoḷi taṉṉai</l>
<l>maṇṇi ṉaimalai yaiyalai nīriṉai mālai māmati yaimaṟai yōrtaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>kaṇṇi ṉaikaṇka ḷāraḷa vumniṉṟu kaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Staying [to fill] my eyes to a full extent, I saw for myself in Kaṇṇamaṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">[the one who is]</l>
<l>Music, the essence that endures in music, the ghee in milk,</l>
<l rend="indent">the sky that endures in massive form,</l>
<l>The splendor of the sun which shines, the sacrifice, the light of a lamp,</l>
<l>The earth, mountains, the crashing sea, wind, the huge moon,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the wisdom of the Vedic experts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
